        <h2>Objectives</h2>
        <p>We aspire to implement the most diverse and effective online payment processor service in Ethiopia with the following specific objectives
Creating a socially responsible enterprise which mainly creates jobs for this tech savvy youth  and variety of domestic manufacturers & retailes.
