Establishing strategic partnership with SMEs, large manufacturers and consumers in the region and in the world based on mutual interest.
Unveiling of very profitable business with multinational ambitions like of Amazontm,Alibabatm e.t.c which engages in both business to consumer and business to business transactions.</p>
        <h2>Expected impacts of our project</h2>
        <p>Expected impact of our proposal resonates with expected impacts from development policies at national level and the NBE directives
The first advanced online retailing platform in Ethiopia responding to needs of end-user communities such as SMEs, large manufacturers and consumers. 
Consideration of societal and gender issues contributing to sustainable development responding polices at national & international level 
Strategic partnership with stakeholder government agencies & associated SMEs and manufacturers in the areas of mutual benefits
A highly successful business with rapid market uptake followed by a sustainable growth </p>

